snippet.title: The Last of Us Part I - Pre-Purchase Trailer | PC
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/the-last-of-us-part-i/

Coming to PC for the first time, experience the emotional storytelling and unforgettable characters in The Last of Us™, winner of over 200 Game of the Year awards.

In a ravaged civilization, where infected and hardened survivors run rampant, Joel, a weary protagonist, is hired to smuggle 14-year-old Ellie out of a military quarantine zone. However, what starts as a small job soon transforms into a brutal cross-country journey.

Pre-purchase now on Steam and the Epic Games Store. 
Available on PC March 3, 2023 

Learn More: https://www.playstation.com/games/the-last-of-us-part-i/

#tlou #thelastofus 

Rated Mature
